<td colspan="3" style="padding-right: 4%">
<p style="font-size:smaller;text-align: right"><cite style="font-style:normal;">—<a href="/wiki/Justus_von_Liebig" title="Justus von Liebig">Justus von Liebig</a> (1855)</cite></p>
</td>
